  92,5,"famma min badhl min malah watqa allah fi dhlk, wsddaq b\"la 'ilh 'iilaa allh\" wama dalat elyh, wama trtb ealayha min aljza', fsnrshdh wnwfqh 'iilaa 'asbab alkhayr walslah wnyssir lah amwrh"
  92,6,"famma min badhl min malah watqa allah fi dhlk, wsddaq b\"la 'ilh 'iilaa allh\" wama dalat elyh, wama trtb ealayha min aljza', fsnrshdh wnwfqh 'iilaa 'asbab alkhayr walslah wnyssir lah amwrh"
  92,7,"famma man badhl min malah watqa allah fi dhlk, wsddaq b\"la 'ilh 'iilaa allh\" wama dalat elyh, wama trtb ealayha min aljza', fsnrshdh wnwfqh 'iilaa 'asbab alkhayr walslah wnyssir lah amwrh"
  92,8,"wama man bakhil bmalh waastaghnaa ean jaza'an rbh, wkdhdhab b\"la 'ilh 'iilaa allh\" wama dalat elyh, wama trtb ealayha min aljza', fsnuyassir lah 'asbab alshqa', wala yanfaeuh malah aldhy bakhil bih 'iidha waqae fi alnar"
  92,9,"wama man bakhil bmalh waastaghnaa ean jaza'an rbh, wkdhdhab b\"la 'ilh 'iilaa allh\" wama dalat elyh, wama trtb ealayha min aljza', fsnuyassir lah 'asbab alshqa', wala yanfaeuh malah aldhy bakhil bih 'iidha waqae fi alnar"
  92,10,"wama man bakhil bmalh waastaghnaa ean jaza'an rbh, wkdhdhab b\"la 'ilh 'iilaa allh\" wama dalat elyh, wama trtb ealayha min aljza', fsnuyassir lah 'asbab alshqa', wala yanfaeuh malah aldhy bakhil bih 'iidha waqae fi alnar"
  92,11,"wama man bakhil bmalh waastaghnaa ean jaza'an rbh, wkdhdhab b\"la 'ilh 'iilaa allh\" wama dalat elyh, wama trtb ealayha min aljza', fsnuyassir lah 'asbab alshqa', wala yanfaeuh malah aldhy bakhil bih 'iidha waqae fi alnar"
  92,12,"'in ealayna bfdlna whkmtna 'ana nbyin tariq alhudaa almawsil 'iilaa allah wjnth min tariq aldlal, wa'iina lana malak alhayat alakhirat walhayat aldnya"
  92,13,"'in ealayna bfdlna whkmtna 'ana nbyin tariq alhudaa almawsil 'iilaa allah wjnth min tariq aldlal, wa'iina lana malak alhayat alakhirat walhayat aldnya"
  92,14,"fhdhdhartkm- 'ayuha alnas- wkhwwaftkm narana ttwhj, wahi nar jhnm"
  92,15,"la ydkhlha 'iilaa man kan shadid alshqa', aladhi kdhdhab nabiin allah mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wslm, wa'aerid ean al'iiman biallah wrswlh, wtaethma"
  92,16,"la ydkhlha 'iilaa man kan shadid alshqa', aladhi kdhdhab nabiin allah mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wslm, wa'aerid ean al'iiman biallah wrswlh, wtaethma"
  92,17,"wsyuzhzah eanha shadid altqwa, aldhy ybdhl malah abtigha' almazid min alkhyr. walays 'iinfaquh dhak mkafat liman asda 'iilayh merwfa, lknh ybtghy bdhlk wajh rabih al'aelaa wrdah, walasawf yetyh allah fi aljanat ma yardaa bh"
